openflap
by Alan Witkowski
https://github.com/jazztickets/openflap

----- HOW TO PLAY -----

Use spacebar, mouseclick, or joystick button to jump.

----- BUILDING -----

-- Dependencies --
CMake 2.8+
SDL2
SDL2_image
SDL2_mixer
SDL2_ttf

-- Building and running --
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make -j`nproc`
cd ../working && ../bin/Release/openflap

-- Installing --
run "sudo make install" from the build directory.

-- Uninstall --
cat install_manifest.txt | xargs sudo rm

Save data is in ~/.local/share/openflap

----- COMMAND-LINE ARGUMENTS -----

Set random number seed:
openflap [32-bit integer]
